Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…螢之助？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與蓓兒丹蒂相遇之後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有時會思考這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天的夢也是某種預兆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:49.07,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H8EB1B7&}{\1c&H004993&}啊啊 各自的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子在整理東西的時候發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爺爺的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爺爺叫「螢之助」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比螢一你帥多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片上的女人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片泛黃了 看不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真知子奶奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像寫了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我一生的光輝就藏於此處」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 螢一 準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種標記的地圖當然就是藏寶圖了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美妙的冒險在等待我們前去！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆電視看多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且馬上就是機車社的合宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒那閒工夫和閒錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒勁～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 貓實工大機車社體能訓練合宿 開始～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼千尋前輩也來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎 因為覺得很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對出合宿費的贊助商有什麼怨言嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這洋房真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房主似乎是爺爺的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話給他 他說可以便宜點租給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了吧 蓓兒丹蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 姐姐 有氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西…在裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了 我是森裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是魔屬的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就送你上西天！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久候大駕 歡迎來到本田莊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是代理負責人本田智惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我們的約定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏 沒想到你還有兩下子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已…已經有了姐姐還…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太骯髒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 這一定是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…你真的不記得我們的約定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說約定了 我根本就不認識你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都不記得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 你們兩位是什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我是很久以前就和森裏先生約定好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上要開會了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在爭風吃醋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫爭風吃醋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天也快黑了 今天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我來準備晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩是思念體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情比較在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念體是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人留下強烈的情感而離開這個世界的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的情感就會聚合成實體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是思念體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽…幽靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來將召開機車社合宿會議！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36號大瀧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始演唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被灌了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也想不起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的和你有過什麼約定嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？為什麼你會有那張照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒 你在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 我決定開自己的店 自力更生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒也嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個紅薯的調味是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 森裏 你去哪兒啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想和蓓兒丹蒂前輩幽會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐剛才不是和大家在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一和那個思念體都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真該盯著她的 她想附身螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念體為了達到目的會不擇手段的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩寇蒂 長谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暈了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開鎖術不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快開門！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在裏面 出來投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 門是打不開的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 快點想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 你和我的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請履行諾言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 鬼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是鬼吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 思念體不是妖魔 退魔程序是不管用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 實現我的願望 否則我決不會放開你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你真的不知道他是誰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:12:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是螢一 不是你所等的螢之助！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和螢之助先生相遇在夏天 僅僅只相處了4天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他與因病來療養的我許下約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我被病魔糾纏之時 那是我精神的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我已經離開人世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但依然一直等待著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他終於來見我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是世代更迭 也有著命運的指引…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我 你和螢之助先生做了怎樣的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我怎麼會睡著了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶你去看樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地下室有什麼讓我看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brough Superier！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}註：Brough Superior SS100AGS\N被稱為"機車中的勞斯萊斯"，全世界只有281台。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼會在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 好像是因為拋錨了所以一直放在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車是你爺爺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:14:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果修好的話 你可以把它騎走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要載我遊湖畔一周
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我和螢之助先生的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了這個 幾十年都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在這裏等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你這句話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為「機車中的勞斯萊斯」的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brough Superior！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！這下我們機車社的財產就不愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物啊寶物 這下賺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的難題是這些人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 這輛車請讓我一個人來修理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？森裏 難道你想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私吞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你想一個人修呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 這輛車必須由我親手修好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運嗎…那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田宮！大瀧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的哮喘舊病復發了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧 小田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…*你來的時候裝在哪裏的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏 這個時代的機車基本上都是著重協調性的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠻特殊的 當心點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要賭氣到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 女神居然被思念體弄暈了 太沒面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是女神 但其實只是個小P孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 真討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了…有一點我沒想明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼知道她和螢一爺爺之間有某種聯繫的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為煮白薯的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮白薯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做的煮白薯的味道和小惠\N教我時煮出來的味道一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂森裏家的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是爺爺的照片和地圖等的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是你的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:17:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這樣好嗎 螢一會被搶走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很瞭解她的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終有一天我也會和螢一…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再跑一周！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人居然乖乖地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛 別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這裏電視的台很少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妨礙我打掃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天衣服幹得真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼女神要作俯臥撐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時放入鮮奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子比較高效率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它說這裏疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣明天就能跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…有件事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得螢之助其實是想回到這裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最終卻沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣而讓你等了幾十年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有後悔過 如果沒有遇到他就好了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病的時候 也曾經怨過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此 與螢之助先生的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍是我一生中最亮的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…一定…比起沒有相識而只是擦身而過…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是像這樣痛苦的相遇 要好得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是對是錯 明天應該就能知道答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拂面而過的輕風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心曠神怡的鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬息而變的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓畏懼病魔的我看的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有這一切的命運 都將是消逝於這風中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…正因如此 與你的的相遇才更快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在這…瞬間即逝的風中才能感受到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢之助先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應我任性的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「再見」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後 好像聽到她這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的寶貝兒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要留下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這是我和她的重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天可能我也會這樣等待蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把這輛機車 為了她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓螢一等幾十年的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就好 我還在想 萬一真要那樣該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊修機車一邊等待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:22:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 再見之時 載著你飛馳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在與你 與這麼多人相遇的這個貓實鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一…我能來到這裏真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 高原的旅社裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍有著一台Brough Superior
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此長眠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 不論何時都想向你傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.34,0:24:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律載著無限的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.73,0:24:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.47,0:24:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 啊啊 喜歡是動搖人心之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.55,0:24:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…喜喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 乾脆點吧！
